Apply
Gunakan konfigurasi saat ini pada master GPU.

Petunjuk:
- Ketika pilihan sinkronisasi setting GPU diaktifkan di tab <General> pada properti advanced, any changes applied to the master GPU are also applied to all similar GPUs installed in the system.
- Always apply the changes you've made before switching to a new master GPU. Any unapplied GPU settings are lost on new master GPU selection.
- Anda dapat menutup tampilan tooltips user interface tooltips via tab <User interface> di properti advanced.